<p><span style="font-size:50%;">sorry if it looks cluttered ive never done this before</span></p>
<hr />
<p>So, on this day - February 8th - last year, I uploaded <a href="/scp-2493">SCP-2493</a>. A year later, his home now has a dossier. Huzzah!</p>
<p>If any authors have an article or skip linked here that they do not want linked, feel free to remove it and post a note saying you don't want it on here. Is all cool.</p>
<p>If an author has made a new article involving Lunar Area 32 that has successfully stuck, feel free to link to said article on here somehow. Leave a message here if you need a hand, etc. (And yes, feel free to use Lunar Area 32 in any of your works. It is encouraged!)</p>

