<p>Lunar Area 32 does cover an area of 12.4&#160;km<sup>2</sup>, but the majority of this is (at least, intended to be) made up of the subterranian portion - the only features of the base visible on the surface are the main reception and the airstrip (both of which were intended to be small), while Sub-Level 1 and onwards are all concealed beneath the surface of Mare Imbrium.</p>
<p>EDIT: Just added a bit to clarify this.</p>

